SELECTION-SCREEN: BEGIN OF BLOCK var WITH FRAME TITLE TEXT-002.
SELECT-OPTIONS: so_carr FOR l_rng_carr_id.
SELECTION-SCREEN: END OF BLOCK var.


AT SELECTION-SCREEN OUTPUT.
  LOOP AT SCREEN.
    "Example for just show the element
    IF screen-name = 'P_RUNDA'.
      screen-input = '0'.
      MODIFY SCREEN.
    ENDIF.
